trans-unit.source: Defines a set of methods and properties used to examine a data source.
trans-unit.target: Definerer et sett med metoder og egenskaper som brukes til å undersøke en datakilde.

trans-unit.source: Classes that implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceSchema> class are used by custom control designer components to provide lists of views in a data source for data-bound controls at design time.
trans-unit.target: Klasser som Implementer den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceSchema>klassen som brukes av egendefinert kontroll designer komponenter oppgi lister med visninger i en datakilde for databundet Kontroller under utformingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceSchema>

trans-unit.source: In a class that is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceSchema>, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceSchema.GetViews%2A> method to get an array of IDataSourceViewSchema objects.
trans-unit.target: I en klasse som er avledet av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceSchema>, bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceSchema.GetViews%2A>metode for å få en matrise av objekter IDataSourceViewSchema.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceSchema.GetViews%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceSchema>

trans-unit.source: Gets an array representing the child views contained in the current view.
trans-unit.target: Henter en matrise som representerer underordnede-visninger som ligger i den gjeldende visningen.

trans-unit.source: It uses its implementation of the GetChildren method to create an array of <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema> objects.
trans-unit.target: Den bruker implementeringen av GetChildren-metoden til å opprette en matrise av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema>

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema"></xref> objects that represent the child views contained in the current view.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema"> </xref> objekter som representerer underordnede-visninger som ligger i den gjeldende visningen.

trans-unit.source: Gets an array containing information about each field in the data source.
trans-unit.target: Henter en matrise som inneholder informasjon om hvert felt i datakilden.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetSchema> class implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema> interface; its implementation of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetViewSchema.GetFields%2A> method returns an array of <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetFieldSchema> objects, each of which derives from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceFieldSchema> interface.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetSchema>klasse implementerer den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema>grensesnittet; implementeringen av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetViewSchema.GetFields%2A>metoden returnerer en matrise av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetFieldSchema>objekter, som er avledet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceFieldSchema>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceFieldSchema> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetFieldSchema> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetViewSchema.GetFields%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetSchema>

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceFieldSchema"></xref> objects representing each of the fields in the data source.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceFieldSchema"> </xref> objekter som representerer alle feltene i datakilden.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the view.
For a <xref:System.Data.DataTable> object, this property corresponds to the <xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: For en <xref:System.Data.DataTable>objekt, samsvarer med denne egenskapen i <xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A> </xref:System.Data.DataTable>
